    dc:description "Figure 10. Male genitalia of Olceclostera jairana sp. nov. A ventral view; B lateral view; C aedeagus, lateral view, apex with two spines; D aedeagus, apex with one spine; E aedeagus, apex with three spines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/955289" ;
